Interface OAuthContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AuthorizationContext

    public interface OAuthContext
extends AuthorizationContext
    The OAuth context which delivers the necessary tokens and identifies the rate and throttle limits
    Restriction
    This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.
